sentences.english: I went to see my friend Janice.
sentences.chinese: 我去看我朋友婕妮斯了。

sentences.english: I saw Jenny going out with Mike when I was walking in the street.
sentences.chinese: 我在街上走着的时候看见婕妮跟麦克约会出去了。

sentences.english: How would Jie Yun deal with the obstacles at the study camp?
sentences.chinese: 婕云该如何应付学习营里的重重难关呢？

sentences.english: Janice wants to get married in August.
sentences.chinese: 婕妮斯想要八月份结婚。

sentences.english: If you clear things up with Jenny, Rose never needs to find out.
sentences.chinese: 如果你跟婕尼把事情搞定，罗斯没必要知道的。

sentences.english: Jenny asked you to record a tape for her.
sentences.chinese: 婕妮叫你帮她录一盘磁带。

sentences.english: When does Janice want to get married?
sentences.chinese: 婕妮斯想要八月份结婚。

sentences.english: If you clear things up with Jenny, Rose will be happy.
sentences.chinese: 如果你把婕尼的事儿搞定，罗斯会很高兴的。

definition: used in the transliteration of people's names
angelica (type of iris)/plant root used in TCM
(phonetic na)/used esp. in female names such as Anna 安娜[An1 na4] or Diana 黛安娜[Dai4 an1 na4]
